{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.1","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 14:1","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.013.034,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">La femme de J\u00e9roboam et le proph\u00e8te Achija<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-18: cf. (1 R 11:28-39; 12:26-33.) 1 R 15:25-30. Jos 23:15. Ps 78:58, 59.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.14.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Dans ce temps-l\u00e0, Abija, fils de J\u00e9roboam, devint malade.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14","name":"1 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.2","name":"1 Rois 14:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.34","name":"1 Rois 13:34","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.13.34"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.2","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 14:2","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.14.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Et J\u00e9roboam dit \u00e0 sa femme: L\u00e8ve-toi, je te prie, et d\u00e9guise-toi pour qu\u2019on ne sache pas que tu es la femme de J\u00e9roboam, et va \u00e0 Silo. Voici, l\u00e0 est Achija, le proph\u00e8te; c\u2019est lui qui m\u2019a dit que je serais roi de ce peuple.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14","name":"1 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.3","name":"1 Rois 14:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.1","name":"1 Rois 14:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.3","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 14:3","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.14.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Prends avec toi dix pains, des g\u00e2teaux et un vase de miel, et entre chez lui; il te dira ce qui arrivera \u00e0 l\u2019enfant.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14","name":"1 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.4","name":"1 Rois 14:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.2","name":"1 Rois 14:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.4","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 14:4","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.14.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>La femme de J\u00e9roboam fit ainsi; elle se leva, alla \u00e0 Silo, et entra dans la maison d\u2019Achija. Achija ne pouvait plus voir, car il avait les yeux fixes par suite de la vieillesse.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14","name":"1 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.5","name":"1 Rois 14:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.3","name":"1 Rois 14:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.5","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 14:5","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.14.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel avait dit \u00e0 Achija: La femme de J\u00e9roboam va venir te consulter au sujet de son fils, parce qu\u2019il est malade. Tu lui parleras de telle et de telle mani\u00e8re. Quand elle arrivera, elle se donnera pour une autre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14","name":"1 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.6","name":"1 Rois 14:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.4","name":"1 Rois 14:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.6","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 14:6","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.14.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Lorsque Achija entendit le bruit de ses pas, au moment o\u00f9 elle franchissait la porte, il dit: Entre, femme de J\u00e9roboam; pourquoi veux-tu te donner pour une autre? Je suis charg\u00e9 de t\u2019annoncer des choses dures.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14","name":"1 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.7","name":"1 Rois 14:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.5","name":"1 Rois 14:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.7","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 14:7","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.14.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Va, dis \u00e0 J\u00e9roboam: Ainsi parle l\u2019\u00c9ternel, le Dieu d\u2019Isra\u00ebl: Je t\u2019ai \u00e9lev\u00e9 du milieu du peuple, je t\u2019ai \u00e9tabli chef de mon peuple d\u2019Isra\u00ebl,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14","name":"1 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.8","name":"1 Rois 14:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.6","name":"1 Rois 14:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.8","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 14:8","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.14.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>j\u2019ai arrach\u00e9 le royaume de la maison de David et je te l\u2019ai donn\u00e9. Et tu n\u2019as pas \u00e9t\u00e9 comme mon serviteur David, qui a observ\u00e9 mes commandements et qui a march\u00e9 apr\u00e8s moi de tout son c\u0153ur, ne faisant que ce qui est droit \u00e0 mes yeux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14","name":"1 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.9","name":"1 Rois 14:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.7","name":"1 Rois 14:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.9","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 14:9","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.14.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Tu as agi plus mal que tous ceux qui ont \u00e9t\u00e9 avant toi, tu es all\u00e9 te faire d\u2019autres dieux, et des images de fonte pour m\u2019irriter, et tu m\u2019as rejet\u00e9 derri\u00e8re ton dos!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14","name":"1 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.10","name":"1 Rois 14:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.8","name":"1 Rois 14:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.10","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 14:10","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.14.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Voil\u00e0 pourquoi je vais faire venir le malheur sur la maison de J\u00e9roboam; j\u2019exterminerai quiconque appartient \u00e0 J\u00e9roboam, celui qui est esclave et celui qui est libre en Isra\u00ebl, et je balaierai la maison de J\u00e9roboam comme on balaie les ordures, jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce qu\u2019elle ait disparu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14","name":"1 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.11","name":"1 Rois 14:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.9","name":"1 Rois 14:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.11","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 14:11","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.14.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Celui de la maison de J\u00e9roboam qui mourra dans la ville sera mang\u00e9 par les chiens, et celui qui mourra dans les champs sera mang\u00e9 par les oiseaux du ciel. Car l\u2019\u00c9ternel a parl\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14","name":"1 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.12","name":"1 Rois 14:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.10","name":"1 Rois 14:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.12","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 14:12","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.14.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Et toi, l\u00e8ve-toi, va dans ta maison. D\u00e8s que tes pieds entreront dans la ville, l\u2019enfant mourra.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14","name":"1 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.13","name":"1 Rois 14:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.11","name":"1 Rois 14:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.13","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 14:13","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.14.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Tout Isra\u00ebl le pleurera, et on l\u2019enterrera; car il est le seul de la maison de J\u00e9roboam qui sera mis dans un s\u00e9pulcre, parce qu\u2019il est le seul de la maison de J\u00e9roboam en qui se soit trouv\u00e9 quelque chose de bon devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel, le Dieu d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14","name":"1 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.14","name":"1 Rois 14:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.12","name":"1 Rois 14:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.14","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 14:14","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.14.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel \u00e9tablira sur Isra\u00ebl un roi qui exterminera la maison de J\u00e9roboam ce jour-l\u00e0. Et n\u2019est-ce pas d\u00e9j\u00e0 ce qui arrive?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14","name":"1 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.15","name":"1 Rois 14:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.13","name":"1 Rois 14:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.15","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 14:15","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.14.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel frappera Isra\u00ebl, et il en sera de lui comme du roseau qui est agit\u00e9 dans les eaux; il arrachera Isra\u00ebl de ce bon pays qu\u2019il avait donn\u00e9 \u00e0 leurs p\u00e8res, et il les dispersera de l\u2019autre c\u00f4t\u00e9 du fleuve, parce qu\u2019ils se sont fait des idoles, irritant l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14","name":"1 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.16","name":"1 Rois 14:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.14","name":"1 Rois 14:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.16","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 14:16","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.14.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Il livrera Isra\u00ebl \u00e0 cause des p\u00e9ch\u00e9s que J\u00e9roboam a commis et qu\u2019il a fait commettre \u00e0 Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14","name":"1 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.17","name":"1 Rois 14:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.15","name":"1 Rois 14:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.17","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 14:17","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.14.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>La femme de J\u00e9roboam se leva, et partit. Elle arriva \u00e0 Thirtsa; et, comme elle atteignait le seuil de la maison, l\u2019enfant mourut.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14","name":"1 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.18","name":"1 Rois 14:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.16","name":"1 Rois 14:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.18","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 14:18","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.14.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>On l\u2019enterra, et tout Isra\u00ebl le pleura, selon la parole que l\u2019\u00c9ternel avait dite par son serviteur Achija, le proph\u00e8te.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14","name":"1 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.19","name":"1 Rois 14:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.17","name":"1 Rois 14:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.19","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 14:19","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.020,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Mort de J\u00e9roboam<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 19-20: cf. 2 Ch 13:2-20. Ec 8:13.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.14.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Le reste des actions de J\u00e9roboam, comment il fit la guerre et comment il r\u00e9gna, cela est \u00e9crit dans le livre des Chroniques des rois d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14","name":"1 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.20","name":"1 Rois 14:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.18","name":"1 Rois 14:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.20","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 14:20","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.14.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>J\u00e9roboam r\u00e9gna vingt-deux ans, puis il se coucha avec ses p\u00e8res. Et Nadab, son fils, r\u00e9gna \u00e0 sa place.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14","name":"1 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.21","name":"1 Rois 14:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.19","name":"1 Rois 14:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.21","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 14:21","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.022,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Le royaume de Juda sous Roboam. \u2014 Idol\u00e2trie. \u2014 Invasion de Schischak, roi d\u2019\u00c9gypte. \u2014 Mort de Roboam<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 21-31: cf. 2 Ch 12. J\u00e9 2:19.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.14.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>\n    Roboam, fils de Salomon, r\u00e9gna sur Juda. Il avait quarante et un ans lorsqu\u2019il devint roi, et il r\u00e9gna dix-sept ans \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem, la ville que l\u2019\u00c9ternel avait choisie sur toutes les tribus d\u2019Isra\u00ebl pour y mettre son nom. Sa m\u00e8re s\u2019appelait Naama, l\u2019Ammonite.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14","name":"1 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.22","name":"1 Rois 14:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.20","name":"1 Rois 14:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.22","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 14:22","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.14.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Juda fit ce qui est mal aux yeux de l\u2019\u00c9ternel; et, par les p\u00e9ch\u00e9s qu\u2019ils commirent, ils excit\u00e8rent sa jalousie plus que ne l\u2019avaient jamais fait leurs p\u00e8res.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14","name":"1 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.23","name":"1 Rois 14:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.21","name":"1 Rois 14:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.23","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 14:23","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.14.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Ils se b\u00e2tirent, eux aussi, des hauts lieux avec des statues et des idoles sur toute colline \u00e9lev\u00e9e et sous tout arbre vert.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14","name":"1 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.24","name":"1 Rois 14:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.22","name":"1 Rois 14:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.24","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 14:24","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.14.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Il y eut m\u00eame des prostitu\u00e9s dans le pays. Ils imit\u00e8rent toutes les abominations des nations que l\u2019\u00c9ternel avait chass\u00e9es devant les enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14","name":"1 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.25","name":"1 Rois 14:25","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.23","name":"1 Rois 14:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.25","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 14:25","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.14.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>La cinqui\u00e8me ann\u00e9e du r\u00e8gne de Roboam, Schischak, roi d\u2019\u00c9gypte, monta contre J\u00e9rusalem.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14","name":"1 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.26","name":"1 Rois 14:26","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.24","name":"1 Rois 14:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.26","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 14:26","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.14.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Il prit les tr\u00e9sors de la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel et les tr\u00e9sors de la maison du roi, il prit tout. Il prit tous les boucliers d\u2019or que Salomon avait faits.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14","name":"1 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.27","name":"1 Rois 14:27","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.25","name":"1 Rois 14:25","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.27","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 14:27","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.14.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>Le roi Roboam fit \u00e0 leur place des boucliers d\u2019airain, et il les remit aux soins des chefs des coureurs, qui gardaient l\u2019entr\u00e9e de la maison du roi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14","name":"1 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.28","name":"1 Rois 14:28","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.26","name":"1 Rois 14:26","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.28","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 14:28","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.14.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>Toutes les fois que le roi allait \u00e0 la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, les coureurs les portaient; puis ils les rapportaient dans la chambre des coureurs.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14","name":"1 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.29","name":"1 Rois 14:29","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.27","name":"1 Rois 14:27","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.29","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 14:29","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.14.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>Le reste des actions de Roboam, et tout ce qu\u2019il a fait, cela n\u2019est-il pas \u00e9crit dans le livre des Chroniques des rois de Juda?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14","name":"1 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.30","name":"1 Rois 14:30","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.28","name":"1 Rois 14:28","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.30","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 14:30","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.14.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>Il y eut toujours guerre entre Roboam et J\u00e9roboam.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14","name":"1 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.31","name":"1 Rois 14:31","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.29","name":"1 Rois 14:29","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.31","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 14:31","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.14.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>Roboam se coucha avec ses p\u00e8res, et il fut enterr\u00e9 avec ses p\u00e8res dans la ville de David. Sa m\u00e8re s\u2019appelait Naama, l\u2019Ammonite. Et Abijam, son fils, r\u00e9gna \u00e0 sa place.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14","name":"1 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.1","name":"1 Rois 15:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.30","name":"1 Rois 14:30","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb28ce933.39364334');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb28ce933.39364334\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb28ce933.39364334","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb28ce933.39364334'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb28ce933.39364334\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}